Demo program
============

Small and simple test program (test.c) and shared library (testlib.c).

libupatch.so will patch a program function [A], a inter-library function
[B] and an internal library variable [C].

libupatch2.so further patches the program function [A'] and library
function [B'].

The program flow is as follows:

  while(1) {
  
    pgm_function		/* program local function */        << [A]
 
				/* libtest.so */
    lib_function		/*   library public function */
  
      lib_private		/*   library private function */    << [B]
      sleep(interval)		                                    << [C]
  
  }
